act.article:
2 Definitions.—In these rules, unless the context otherwise requires,—
a “Chairperson” means the Chairperson of the Review Committee constituted under sub-section (1) of section 60 of the Ordinance1;
b “member” means the member of the Review Committee constituted under sub-section (1) of section 60 of the Ordinance1;
c “Ordinance”1 means the Prevention of Terrorism (Second) Ordinance, 20011 (12 of 2001);
d all other words and expressions used in these rules but not defined in these rules and defined in the Ordinance1 shall have the meanings respectively assigned to them in the Ordinance1.
